content.title: RHEA-2015:1076: Red Hat JBoss Enterprise Application Platform 6.4.1 update on RHEL 5 (Low)
content.description:
Red Hat JBoss Enterprise Application Platform 6 is a platform for Java
applications based on JBoss Application Server 7.

This release updates and replaces Red Hat JBoss Enterprise Application
Platform 6.4 and includes bug fixes and enhancements. Documentation for these
changes is in the Red Hat JBoss Enterprise Application Platform 6.4.1
Release Notes, linked to in the References.

All users of Red Hat JBoss Enterprise Application Platform 6.4 on Red Hat
Enterprise Linux 5 are advised to upgrade to these updated packages. The
JBoss server process must be restarted for the update to take effect.
